Currently we have implemetned the Customer Alerts API for CTA



See more information here: http://www.transitchicago.com/developers/alerts.aspx

API Locations
 •Route Status API
http://www.transitchicago.com/api/1.0/routes.aspx
 Gives the status of a route based on the most significant event presently affecting service on that route, as a well-formed XML document.
  
•Detailed Alerts API
http://www.transitchicago.com/api/1.0/alerts.aspx
 Gives detailed information about individual alerts, including descriptive text, as a well-formed XML document.

 